{"tid":836804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"在香港,吃飯的時候我們不拉屎","createTime":"2018-09-26T02:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T03:59:45.000Z","uid":59844,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b9314ec88cd5188d80bac5b254bd6c5f9279366b","tid":836804,"uid":59844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:18:07.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以張瑞典果條片拍條廣東話版? <br />\n等中國將香港列為旅遊警示國家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e9329b6ec1bd5e5a2dcee52469c3c134897c15","tid":836804,"uid":10692,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:30:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edd3784e67928f697149ca709f64eda95ec9eddd","tid":836804,"uid":38523,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b7e9329b6ec1bd5e5a2dcee52469c3c134897c15","tid":836804,"uid":10692,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:30:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:31:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">福氣來</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">住屋住到生癌真係世界首創<br />\n搵幾多隻奶波魔魔上來踩港都冇用<br />\n</span></span><br />\n奶波魔魔家屬示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/103744_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F103744_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=45c1f1e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n［有線中國組］內地租盤甲醛超標 租戶入住兩月患白血病 三日後身亡</span></span><br />\n<br />\n國內最大長租公寓營運商自如早前被指推高北京房租後，再陷入甲醛超標的風波。<br />\n<br />\n一名阿里巴巴員工5月初搬入自如在杭州出租的房間，兩個月後確診患上白血病，接著在短短三日後去世。妻子到他生前住所進行空氣檢測，發現屋內多處甲醛濃度超標，懷疑同死因有關。<br />\n<br />\n消息一出，紛紛有自如租戶在自己單位進行測試，發現甲醛超標不是個別例子；更有受甲醛超標影響的自如租戶退租後，發現自如將有問題單位再出租。<br />\n<br />\n自如一方面發聲明強調所有裝修材料和家具等都符合國家標準，但又同時在全國收回所有首次出租的租盤。他們表示會在百分百檢測合格後，才重新出租；亦會向6月1日後，入住首次出租盤的租戶提供空氣檢測服務。若證實有超標問題，可無條件退租和換租。<br />\n<br />\n本身隸屬鏈家集團的自如靠著收樓、裝修再轉租出去的盈利模式，迅速發展起來。到了今時今日，業務遍布包括北上廣深在內的九個城市，擁有超70萬個租盤，租戶達160萬人。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n你以為死左就有得安樂？<br />\n推火葬強挖棺材燒屍！<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/132238_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F132238_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3a85dc47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">福氣來</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏</span></span>"},{"pid":"082892b7989cc3d5a71a01f34f33c1c9efd52e2c","tid":836804,"uid":195350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:32:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0c0932129942fcc60f4d0afa5c8b0d516cbe9bc3","tid":836804,"uid":17765,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/103244_fd6ce1108c8a9b08cb2f9ced64b74706.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F103244_fd6ce1108c8a9b08cb2f9ced64b74706.png&h=627c8843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想問呢個標誌幾時會周街都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d95f753ff8fb80e70f0963fce1f351dca383d5","tid":836804,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆